<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.4.6">
<l>kūttar kuṭameṭut tāṭil kōvinta ṉāmeṉa vōṭum</l>
<l>vāytta kuḻalōcai kēṭkiṉ māyava ṉeṉṟumai yākku</l>
<l>māycciyar veṇṇeykaḷ kāṇi lavaṉuṇṭa veṇṇeyī teṉṉum</l>
<l>pēycci mulaicuvait tāṟkeṉ peṇkoṭi yēṟiya pittē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When dancers set up a pot [and] dance she runs, saying  “it is Kōvintaṉ”,</l>
<l>when she hears she sound of an excellent(?) flute, she is perplexed, saying “the Dark one”,</l>
<l>when she sees the cowherdesses’ butter she says “this [is] the butter he ate”,</l>
<l>[thus] the infatuation that has risen in my creeper daughter towards him who tasted the breast of the demoness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
